STATE
v.
Nathaniel PHILLIPS. No. 165P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. James Rainsford, Hillsborough, for Phillips, Nathaniel Paige. Melody R. Hairston, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. James R. Woodall, Jr., District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of May 2015 by Defendant for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Dissolved by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
